 DRC</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">.  Not </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">only are smuggled wild primat</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">es kept as pets, but local and international businesses, such </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">as hotels, bars, and restaurants, buy them hoping to attract customers by capitalizing (f</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">or example, by using them</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt"> as a photographic “prop”) on the trend of privately owned</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt"> primat</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">es, helping create an associated market for “performing”</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt"> primate</span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">s.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="8" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt; list-style-position:inside; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-indent:-18pt"><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Role </span><span style="font-family:'Century Schoolbook'; font-size:12pt; font-we